collectible.name: Liminal Composition #1
collectible.description: One of a series of four 1-of-1 pieces by Anton Siena, exploring the very edge of consciousness – indeed, of perception itself.  Where reality gives way to… what?  The void?  Or a higher plane – a parallel realm of conscious understanding – an elevated window onto reality – a light shining on the truth of what it is to be, whether in-world, IRL, or within the depths of our very soul.

collectible.name: Golden Seahorse
collectible.description:
Wearables created by Yumika.

Seahorses are called Tatsu-no-Otoshigo, meaning the child dropped by the dragon.

A golden seahorse, a fitting tribute to the New Year's celebration, has been spawned by a dragon in the sky.
Whoever gets it may be blessed with good health and a leap forward.
